<<<<<Small Description>>>>> Lightweight PyTorch Deep Learning Environment with Essential DL Stack <<<<</Small Description>>>>>
========================================================================================
<<<<<Description>>>>> This is a lightweight container optimized for PyTorch deep learning model development and research. The environment includes only essential libraries to minimize container size while providing a complete deep learning stack. It features PyTorch with CUDA support, essential data science libraries, and Jupyter Lab for interactive development. The container is designed for efficient GPU-accelerated deep learning workflows with minimal overhead.

Key Features:
- Python with PyTorch ecosystem (torch, torchvision, torchaudio)
- CUDA support for GPU acceleration
- PyTorch Lightning for structured training
- Essential data science stack (NumPy, Pandas, Scikit-learn)
- Visualization tools (Matplotlib, Seaborn)
- Development environment (Jupyter Lab, IPython)
- Optimized cache settings for temporary directories
- Extensible design for adding domain-specific packages <<<<</Description>>>>>
