<<<<<Included Packages>>>>> The container ships with a deep learning and data science stack pre-installed, so most workflows work out of the box with no extra setup. This is a representative list of the core packages present across builds of this container family, not the full install — run a shell inside the container and use `pip list` to see everything actually installed in a given build.

